      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Looking for a reliable ride that's ready for its next adventure? I\u2019m parting with my trusty car, and it\u2019s still in really solid shape! It\u2019s been great to me, runs smoothly, and is perfect for daily commutes or fun weekend road trips. It\u2019s got plenty of life left and is just waiting for a new owner to take the wheel. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a good home!",
