    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six engine. This high-revving power unit utilizes individual throttle bodies and Double-VANOS variable valve timing to produce a visceral 333 hp. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox and a mechanical limited-slip differential. To address common platform weaknesses, this chassis has received structural subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive Vanos bulletproofing. The suspension maintains its factory-intended kinematics with refreshed bushings and Sachs dampers. Though the exterior displays minor road-derived patina, the mechanical vitals remain robust, including recent rod bearing service and a valve clearance adjustment. A true driver\u2019s specification for those who prioritize longitudinal and lateral dynamics.",
      "price": 33800.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
