    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2019 Audi A6 3.0T Premium Plus, a sophisticated sedan that offers a perfect blend of performance and luxury. The exterior is finished in a striking Mythos Black Metallic; while it shows some light peppering on the front bumper from highway commuting, the paint retains a high-gloss finish and is free of any major dents or scratches. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of Nougat Brown leather and natural wood inlays. The interior is in excellent shape with no tears in the upholstery, and all technological features\u2014including the Audi Virtual Cockpit, 360-degree camera, and the Bang & Olufsen premium sound system\u2014are fully operational. Mechanically, this vehicle is robust. It has followed a strict factory maintenance schedule, with the most recent service including a fresh oil change, new cabin filters, and a comprehensive multi-point inspection. The Quattro all-wheel-drive system provides exceptional grip, and the turbocharged V6 engine runs smoothly without any hesitation. This car has been garage-kept, smoke-free, and is ready for its next owner to enjoy a premium driving experience without the new-car price tag.",
      "price": 32500.0,
